Package decoworld.protocol.accounts

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountRequests
    AccountRequests is the abstract supertype for all account-related requests.
    AccountRequests.FetchUserRequest
    FetchUserRequest is the message that will be sent from a client to the server when a client wishes to fetch a User model from the server.
    AccountRequests.LoginRequest
    LoginRequest is the message that will be sent from a client to the server when a user makes a login attempt.
    AccountRequests.RegisterUserRequest
    RegisterUserRequest is the message that will be sent from a client to the server when a user attempts to register as a new user.
    AccountRequests.UpdateUserRequest
    UpdateUserRequest is the message that will be sent from a client to the server when a client wishes to update a User model on the server.
    AccountResponses
    AccountResponses is the abstract supertype for all account-related responses.
    AccountResponses.FetchUserResponse
    Response from a FetchUserRequest.
    AccountResponses.LoginFailure
    Message to be passed from the server's LoginManager to a client who had made a login request, to notify it that the request was unsuccessful.
    AccountResponses.LoginSuccess
    Message to be passed from the server's LoginManager to a client who had made a login request, to notify it that the request was successful.
    AccountResponses.RegisterUserResponse
    Response from a RegisterUserRequest.
    AccountResponses.UpdateUserResponse
    Reponse from an UpdateUserRequest.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AccountRequests.RegisterUserError
    List of possible errors when attempting to process a registration request Needs to sit in the protocol as client and server both need to be able to reference the enums.
